PART 1: THE RESONANCE CASCADE IN B_m(x)
======================================================================

B_m = (2+x)·B_{m-1} - B_{m-2}

This recurrence is a SECOND-ORDER LINEAR DIFFERENCE EQUATION.
It describes a resonance cascade where each 'level' m amplifies
the previous two levels by the coupling constant (2+x).

